## Verification Plan

| # | Scenario | Expected |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | New student `/start` | Step-by-step form: name → phone → parent phone |
| 2 | Select available group | "تم ارسال طلبك وجاري المراجعة" |
| 3 | Select full group | "ممتلئة" + waitlist offer |
| 4 | Join waitlist | Saved, confirmation shown |
| 5 | "No suitable time" | Bot prompts for preferred time, saves as `general` |
| 6 | Existing user `/start` | Shows name + group + Arabic status |
| 7 | Admin `/admin` | Lists all pending with Approve/Reject buttons |
| 8 | Admin approves | Student receives approval notification |
| 9 | Admin rejects | Student receives rejection notification |
| 10 | Student changes group | Old booking cancelled, waitlist for that group notified |
